Mesh generation code:

Calculates the vertices, number of triangles, number of side's mesh edges and total edges.
Using 3 different keys in hach_find and hach_add one can test the average and max collision rate.

Calculates quality of triangles through msh_tri_quality_Q1 and msh_tri_quality_Q2

Computes the neighbors with msh_neighbors using a Hach table



To compile/Compute do: 

cd src/
make clean
make
cd ..
./src/mesh data/carre_4h.mesh